1
00:01:09,880 --> 00:01:11,140
Let go of your grudges.

2
00:01:12,240 --> 00:01:13,160
Start over.

3
00:01:14,960 --> 00:01:16,400
Do I really have a chance?

4
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:19,600
No.

5
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:06,850
Tell me about it.

6
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:09,580
Fifteen years ago,

7
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:14,560
my father died because of Ye Qiming.

8
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:17,600
Look.

9
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,780
These workers have it so hard.

10
00:02:19,920 --> 00:02:21,000
You can't do this.

11
00:02:21,880 --> 00:02:23,560
The boss above didn't pay me.

12
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,130
What do you want me to do?

13
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,160
I have no money.

14
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:27,900
But it's your project.

15
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:30,320
They will definitely ask you for money.

16
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:31,920
Don't just stand there.

17
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:33,720
Figure out a way to ask for money.

18
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:36,370
It was Ye Qiming and those country folk

19
00:02:36,480 --> 00:02:38,280
who drove my father to his death.

20
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:40,480
It's perfectly justified for them to ask for their wages back.

21
00:02:40,480 --> 00:02:44,480
The one who drove your father to his death was the boss who owed the money.

22
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:46,380
You know that better than I do.

23
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:48,960
You've been deceiving yourself all along.

24
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:51,640
You can't direct your hatred towards those

25
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:52,700
in the upper class,

26
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:55,780
so you can only bully the vulnerable groups.

27
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:57,360
But have you ever thought

28
00:02:57,560 --> 00:03:00,560
that your father was also a part of a vulnerable group?

29
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:04,580
You've driven father after father to death,

30
00:03:04,600 --> 00:03:06,860
and they have daughters of their own too.

31
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:09,520
They got what they deserved.

32
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:11,240
Who the boss that owed money is,

33
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,440
I think you must know.

34
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:15,210
He's under Liu Weishan's protection.

35
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,079
And yet you treat Liu Weishan

36
00:03:17,079 --> 00:03:18,280
like your own father.

37
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:21,980
Bear the consequences you ought to bear.

38
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:03,280
Shen Feng.

39
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,120
Wake up.

40
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:07,540
Captain Jiang.

41
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:08,560
You're awake.

42
00:04:10,320 --> 00:04:11,180
How do you feel?

43
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:14,280
Did I get knocked silly?

44
00:04:15,040 --> 00:04:16,570
Why does my head hurt so much

45
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:18,200
whenever I move it?

46
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:21,050
I talked to the doctor a bit.

47
00:04:23,840 --> 00:04:25,970
The situation isn't very optimistic.

48
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:28,880
There's a bit of intracranial hemorrhage.

49
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:32,840
You might be paralyzed.

50
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:34,600
Really?

51
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,240
I just read the report.

52
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,100
The doctor said

53
00:04:40,159 --> 00:04:41,760
all indicators are pretty good.

54
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:42,960
You can be discharged after a few days of rest.

55
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:44,040
But because of the concussion,

56
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:45,300
you still need to rest.

57
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:48,080
That's great.

58
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:51,460
What are you doing?

59
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:54,080
I just want to hurry back to the bureau

60
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:55,360
and close this case.

61
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:56,960
It's already closed.

62
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:59,360
Xiao Li is writing the final report.

63
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:00,360
I have to say,

64
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:02,860
your apprentice has really grown up.

65
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:04,400
Being able to save you this time

66
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:05,730
is all thanks to Xiao Li.

67
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:07,920
We really owe it to him this time.

68
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:08,920
We got you out

69
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:11,260
because he pinpointed our location.

70
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:12,640
Wait a minute.

71
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:16,240
We couldn't contact the outside at that time.

72
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:17,840
How did he know where we were?

73
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:20,460
Xiao Li.

74
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:22,600
Captain Jiang has been kidnapped.

75
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:24,530
He's at a warehouse in the suburbs.

76
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:27,160
I'll try to tell you the exact location.

77
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:32,320
After I arrived at the scene,

78
00:05:32,320 --> 00:05:34,050
I talked to Xiao Li on the phone,

79
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:36,600
but the call was never disconnected.

80
00:05:37,440 --> 00:05:38,440
Do you remember the Morse code

81
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:40,300
we learned in the police academy?

82
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:41,600
I used that

83
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:43,800
to communicate with Xiao Li step by step

84
00:05:43,840 --> 00:05:46,320
and tell him the exact location of the suspects and me.

85
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:46,850
Retreat.

86
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:47,770
Retreat.

87
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:31,480
Move.

88
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:40,960
Shen Feng.

89
00:06:42,320 --> 00:06:43,680
I want an apple.

90
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:45,090
I'll get one for you.

91
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:46,240
Okay.

92
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:56,200
The doctor just told me...

93
00:06:57,080 --> 00:07:00,140
that eating apples with the skin on is more nutritious.

94
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:02,560
Okay.

95
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:04,010
Then I'll ask the doctor

96
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:06,080
if Shen Feng should only eat the core from now on.

97
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:08,120
I... I'll buy a peeler and come back later.

98
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:09,200
According to the latest reports,

99
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:11,080
the city's July 25 severed arm case has been solved.

100
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:11,560
Come.

101
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:13,200
Ye Qiming of Tongda Group

102
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:15,480
bribed Kuai to kill Tian Liang,

103
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:18,680
intending to frame Liu Weishan, president of Xincheng Group.

104
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:21,160
When Yu Na sent Chen Hao to Tian Liang's house,

105
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,680
Tian Liang was already dead.

106
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:24,680
Yu Na ordered Chen Hao to handle it properly.

107
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:26,240
Chen Hao dismembered the body.

108
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:28,080
After the police's meticulous investigation,

109
00:07:28,080 --> 00:07:30,480
the truth of the case finally came to light.

110
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:32,720
College student Lu Yang was caught in a honey trap

111
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:33,760
and urgently needed money.

112
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:36,480
He got evidence of Tian Liang's multiple affairs,

113
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:39,000
and used it to blackmail Ye Qiming of Tongda Group.

114
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:42,040
Afraid that Lu Yang would be involved in Tian Liang's case,

115
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:44,840
Yu Na hired Qian Yong to kill him.

116
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:47,800
Ye Qiming of Tongda Group indeed died by suicide.

117
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,200
The police also found out

118
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:51,159
that five years ago, reporter Song Qing,

119
00:07:51,159 --> 00:07:53,480
who was collecting evidence of Liu Weishan's crimes,

120
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,520
was silenced.

121
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:57,240
The USB drive she risked her life to send out was found,

122
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:59,600
confirming the evidence of Liu Weishan's crimes.

123
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,960
Liu Weishan has been arrested.

124
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:02,440
His confessed crimes

125
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,560
include hiring a hitman to kill Song Qing

126
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:06,560
and forcing Ye Qiming to commit suicide.

127
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,520
This case.

128
00:08:08,440 --> 00:08:10,360
Many people were involved in the case.

129
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:13,520
The criminal acts have caused an extremely bad

130
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:14,460
social impact.

131
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:16,840
The solving of the July 25 major case

132
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:19,160
undoubtedly gave the public

133
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:21,600
a shot in the arm.

134
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:23,440
The organization decided

135
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:27,320
to award all comrades of the July 25 task force

136
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:29,440
a collective commendation.

137
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:31,440
In our future work,

138
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:34,360
we must continue to maintain

139
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:38,000
a highly responsible attitude toward the public,

140
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:41,120
go all out to solve all kinds of cases,

141
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:45,360
safeguard the lives and property of the public,

142
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:48,560
and ensure long-term public security.

143
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:54,800
Everyone, stop your work for a moment.

144
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:56,800
Let's have a quick meeting to summarize our experience.

145
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:57,260
Come on.

146
00:08:58,640 --> 00:08:59,240
Hurry up.

147
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:06,520
Shen Feng.

148
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,260
Where is Shen Feng?

149
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:19,160
Captain Shen

150
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,580
should have gone back.

151
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:23,620
Where did he go?

152
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:24,400
Master,

153
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,440
where is Brother Shen?

154
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:28,920
He was specially transferred to our team for this case.

155
00:09:28,920 --> 00:09:30,450
Now that the case is closed,

156
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:32,500
isn't it normal for him to go back?

157
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:33,940
You managed to find me.

158
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:37,650
You didn't show up for the meeting.

159
00:10:40,520 --> 00:10:41,360
Well,

160
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:45,650
I'm not part of the task force anymore.

161
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:52,010
Thanks for your help this time.

162
00:10:56,280 --> 00:10:56,920
For what?

163
00:10:58,920 --> 00:10:59,520
Thanks

164
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:05,580
for everything recently.

165
00:11:10,800 --> 00:11:11,330
Anytime.

166
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:18,220
Why don't you come back to the frontline?

167
00:11:18,280 --> 00:11:21,080
I feel like you're not really suited for a desk job.

168
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:29,320
Here,

169
00:11:38,520 --> 00:11:39,650
transfer to my unit.

170
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:44,680
Sure.
